Package: archetyper
Type: Package
Title: Generates a project template for data mining projects
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Michael Korvink
Maintainer: Michael Korvink <mkorvink@protonmail.com>
Description: The archetyper project generates a set of components and directories to manage the data mining workflow as well as peripheral components to support unit testing, source control, logging, externalized properties, and linting.     
